0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"大炮工作流使用说明","properties":{"ue_properties":{"version":"7.5.2","widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["# 🌈              资源说明  提示词优化参考          🌈\n---\n# 严格正面证件照构图：头部与身体完全正对镜头，双眼平视，面部对称居中（鼻梁/下巴/领口中轴对齐），双耳完整露出；头发全部向后梳理披肩，确保不遮挡耳朵、肩膀和身体轮廓；双肩严格水平（锁骨连线平行画框，Y轴误差≤5像素），无任何侧身倾斜；穿着合体女士西装；保持原生五官，皮肤自然白皙（色值#FFF5F5）；纯红背景（#FF0000），高清画质无阴影，分辨率≥300DPI\n\n# Create a strict front-facing passport photo composition: the head and body should be perfectly aligned and facing the camera, with the eyes looking straight ahead. The face must be symmetrical and centered, with the nose, chin, and collarline aligned along the vertical axis. Ensure both ears are fully visible. The hair should be styled back and fall over the shoulders, making sure it doesn't block the ears, shoulders, or body outline. The shoulders should be perfectly level (clavicle line parallel to the frame, Y-axis deviation ≤ 5 pixels), with no tilting to the sides. The subject should wear a well-fitting women's suit. Maintain the natural facial features with fair skin (#FFF5F5) and a pure red background (#FF0000). The image should have no shadows, be in high definition, and have a resolution of at least 300 DPI."],"color":"#2a363b","bgcolor":"#3f5159"},{"id":115,"type":"SimpleMath+","pos":[3207.1909264587366,718.4710729309027],"size":[210,98],"flags":{"collapsed":true},"order":17,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"A","name":"a","shape":7,"type":"*","link":115},{"localized_name":"B","name":"b","shape":7,"type":"*","link":null},{"localized_name":"c","name":"c","shape":7,"type":"*","link":null},{"localized_name":"值","name":"value","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"value"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"label":"整数","localized_name":"整数","name":"INT","type":"INT","links":[125]},{"label":"浮点","localized_name":"浮点","name":"FLOAT","type":"FLOAT","links":null}],"properties":{"Node name for S&R":"SimpleMath+","cnr_id":"comfyui_essentials","ver":"9d9f4bedfc9f0321c19faf71